{"tid":869022,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過 茶記食飯 D野好耐冇黎","createTime":"2018-10-20T04:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T05:47:57.000Z","uid":185263,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b84cb326cfc17377116d3a9e797dd6c48b1f4d4b","tid":869022,"uid":185263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:22:50.000Z","msg":"頭先真係嬲，去茶記食個餐，等左成20 分鐘仲未黎，見佢哋響到搞緊大生意大量外賣， 好自然我就走，D人就叫住我，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 店員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 先生你落咗order唔可以走㗎喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你啲嘢咁耐未送嚟，梗係走啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁唔得㗎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你而家比到嘢我食我咪留低囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔可以走㗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我奪門而出，拜拜你條尾。<br />\n大家會唔會一樣咁做？"},{"pid":"011b23562abf686125368fce25ae549a4685f264","tid":869022,"uid":45537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"會 仲會屌撚爆佢"},{"pid":"68f4afee50c39ae7fc9c7130d4f878061e8d295c","tid":869022,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"咁你咪蝕咗餐飯錢"},{"pid":"1fa009d21710e8f05c331049ce3dcbcabf2faf8a","tid":869022,"uid":185263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68f4afee50c39ae7fc9c7130d4f878061e8d295c","tid":869022,"uid":13065,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T04:30:19.000Z","msg":"咁你咪蝕咗餐飯錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T05:34:32.000Z","msg":"食茶記當然食完先比㗎"},{"pid":"f745666b12e7aba62954e42f566708a9f5676968","tid":869022,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci